    "Handling the complexity of multilingual voice safety classification.",
    "Balancing model accuracy with computational efficiency to support large-scale deployment.",
    "Managing the trade-off between model size and performance, especially for multilingual and multitask architectures."
  ],
  "ai_future_directions": [
    "Extending models with multilingual training data to support a wider range of languages and language mixing.",
