    "summary": "DoorDash's commitment to providing transparent and accurate information has led to the development of advanced predictive models that enhance ETA precision. By embracing multi-task models, deep learning, and probabilistic forecasts, DoorDash is producing world-class predictions while accounting for real-world uncertainties.",
