      "answer": "Future work includes developing a more fine-grained real-time sequence signal with additional action types and metadata, improving GPU serving usability and performance, continuing model iteration to fully utilize real-time signals, and expanding the application of similar ideas to other surfaces such as related pins, notifications, and search."
