      "User interactions such as clicks and favorites are more predictive of purchase intent than cart adds or purchases.",
      "Personalization introduces latency challenges due to the need to rank items for every user-query pair.",
      "Privacy considerations are important, and the system must balance personalization with user preferences and data sensitivity."
